{
  "stem": "15768.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was her work behind the scenes and, of course, Herbert's work behind the scenes that made it possible for us to get out.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had no-- we-- we had no papers from the American consulate that would have said that we were en route to the United States.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I know that at one point before we left, there was a bit of hysteria, and my mother actually bought papers, or passages for all four of us, for a good deal of money, to go to Cuba.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If all else failed, we would have gone that route.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I wonder.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But at any rate, it was supposed to be sort of a little backup in case everything else went wrong.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so then we were in Belgium.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were reunited with my father.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we lived in a--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It must have been-- I-- I don't recall because he met us-- he met us when we got there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As I understand from my cousin, it was this-- this business associate in-- in Spa that somehow worked it out that he was released from jail.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in Spa, we-- we sort of languished for a bit [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] until perhaps early in June when we decided to move to Brussels because Spa was so close to the border that both my mother and father felt fairly uncomfortable-- in case something were to go wrong that we would be of-- further inland.",
      "word_count": 58
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Spa, it was more or less carefree.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We did not go to school in Spa.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so we-- we played as children will and were in the park and lived in a furnished room and didn't have much.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was not much going on at the time as far as we children were concerned.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
